dc_title_s: West Indies, Caribbean Sea, Anegada Passage with adjacent islands (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: Prepared and published by the Defense Mapping Agency Hydrographic/Topographic Center. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by spot heights. "From U.S. and British surveys to 1976 with additions from a Netherlands chart of 1973." "Copyright 1993 by the United States Government. No copyright claimed under Title 17 U.S.C." "Soundings in meters." Includes compilation diagram. Map No. 25600. This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
